---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy | Lindisfarn"
  description="How Lindisfarn collects, uses, and protects your personal information. PIPEDA-compliant privacy practices."
>
  <section class="relative px-6 py-20 md:py-28 bg-[#F2F0E9]">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-24">
      
      <!-- Header -->
      <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[#2D5016] mb-4 font-['JetBrains_Mono',monospace]">
        Legal
      </p>
      
      <h1 class="font-['Cormorant_Garamond',serif] text-4xl md:text-5xl text-[#2B2B2B] mb-3">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-[#4A5A66] font-['JetBrains_Mono',monospace] text-sm mb-12 pb-8 border-b border-[#2B2B2B]/10">
        Last Updated: January 27, 2026
      </p>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="space-y-8 font-['EB_Garamond',serif] text-lg text-[#2B2B2B] leading-relaxed">
        
        <p>
          At Lindisfarn, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This policy explains what we collect, why we collect it, and how we keep it safe—in plain English.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-['Cormorant_Garamond',serif] text-2xl md:text-3xl text-[#2B2B2B] mt-10 mb-4">
          What We Collect
        </h2>
        
        <p>When you sign up as a Founding Member or contact us, we collect:</p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Name</strong> — so we know who you are</li>
          <li><strong>Email</strong> — our primary way to reach you</li>
          <li><strong>Phone Number</strong> — for pickup coordination</li>
          <li><strong>Address</strong> — for our records and potential delivery</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>
          This information is collected through Zoho Forms and stored securely in our Zoho account.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-['Cormorant_Garamond',serif] text-2xl md:text-3xl text-[#2B2B2B] mt-10 mb-4">
          Payment Information
        </h2>
        
        <p>
          All payments are processed by <strong>Stripe</strong>. We never see, store, or have access to your credit card numbers. Stripe handles everything securely and is PCI-DSS compliant.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-['Cormorant_Garamond',serif] text-2xl md:text-3xl text-[#2B2B2B] mt-10 mb-4">
          Website Analytics
        </h2>
        
        <p>We use the following tools to understand how visitors use our website:</p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Facebook Pixel</strong> — helps us measure the effectiveness of our outreach</li>
          <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — tells us how many people visit and what pages they view</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>
          These tools collect anonymous data about your visit (pages viewed, time on site, general location). They do not identify you personally unless you submit a form.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-['Cormorant_Garamond',serif] text-2xl md:text-3xl text-[#2B2B2B] mt-10 mb-4">
          How We Use Your Information
        </h2>
        
        <p>We use your information to:</p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Process and confirm your membership</li>
          <li>Send order updates and pickup notifications</li>
          <li>Share our seasonal farm newsletter (you can unsubscribe anytime)</li>
          <li>Respond to your questions</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p class="font-semibold text-[#2D5016]">
          We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes. Ever.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-['Cormorant_Garamond',serif] text-2xl md:text-3xl text-[#2B2B2B] mt-10 mb-4">
          Your Rights
        </h2>
        
        <p>Under Canadian privacy law (PIPEDA), you have the right to:</p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Know what information we have about you</li>
          <li>Request corrections to your information</li>
          <li>Ask us to delete your information</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent for communications</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>
          To exercise any of these rights, simply email us. We're a small farm—we'll respond personally.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-['Cormorant_Garamond',serif] text-2xl md:text-3xl text-[#2B2B2B] mt-10 mb-4">
          Data Security
        </h2>
        
        <p>
          We take reasonable measures to protect your information, including secure form submission (HTTPS), trusted third-party services (Zoho, Stripe), and limiting access to your data to only those who need it.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-['Cormorant_Garamond',serif] text-2xl md:text-3xl text-[#2B2B2B] mt-10 mb-4">
          Contact Us
        </h2>
        
        <p>
          Questions about this policy? Reach out:
        </p>
        
        <p class="font-['JetBrains_Mono',monospace] text-base text-[#4A5A66]">
          Lindisfarn<br/>
          Glen Robertson, Ontario<br/>
          Email: hello@lindisfarn.com
        </p>

      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="py-16 text-center border-t border-[#2B2B2B]/10 bg-[#F2F0E9]">
    <p class="font-['Cormorant_Garamond',serif] text-2xl italic text-[#4A5A66]">
      Ora et Labora
    </p>
    
    <div class="flex justify-center gap-6 mt-8">
      <a href="/privacy" class="text-[#4A5A66] text-xs font-['JetBrains_Mono',monospace] hover:text-[#C8A97E] transition-colors">
        Privacy Policy
      </a>
      <a href="/terms" class="text-[#4A5A66] text-xs font-['JetBrains_Mono',monospace] hover:text-[#C8A97E] transition-colors">
        Terms & Conditions
      </a>
    </div>
    
    <p class="text-[#4A5A66] text-xs mt-6">
      © 2026 Lindisfarn · Glen Robertson, Ontario
    </p>
  </footer>
</Layout>
